Package org.eclipse.rwt

Interface Summary
Adaptable Adaptable objects lets you add interfaces to a class and lets clients query whether an object has a particular extension.
AdapterFactory Deprecated. This class was made API accidientially and will be removed in future releases.
IBrowserHistory This interface provides methods to use the browser's history for navigating within the application.
 

Class Summary
RWT This class provides access to aspects of RWT which are not part of the SWT API as RAP needs some additions regarding the server and client communication.
RWT.NLS This utility class helps to provide a similar approach for compile safe native language support than NLS does.
SessionSingletonBase SessionSingletonBase creates and manages a unique instance of a given type with session scope.
